      <title>波兰利率委员会关系紧张，行长寻求推迟降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/polish-rate-panel-tensions-fray-as-governor-seeks-to-delay-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰政策制定者与央行行长亚当格拉宾斯基 (Adam Glapinski) 的观点保持距离，后者认为明年可能不会降息，这一分歧在该国经济放缓之际显现出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/polish-rate-panel-tensions-fray-as-governor-seeks-to-delay-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 13:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
